Documentation Generator Plugins API

This is the API for the docJGenerator plugins framework.

See: Description

Packages 
Package Description
org.docgene.model
Contains the documentation model.
org.docgene.parser
Contains the classes which handle the parsing of the documentation directory.
org.docgene.plugins
Contains the classes which manage the Plugins.
org.docgene.writer
Contains the classes which write the html documentation files from the documentation model.
